content.value:
Your water at the right time, in the right place. Appia is a French spring water, known for its nutritional qualities. Appia is an elegant object and its ergonomic design is reusable.
Appia isthe result of a group cohesion. A team of 6 communicators and designers.

I imagined and deployed the brand identity, print and digital. The art direction was thought for the creation of the logo, packaging, labels, website, as well as for the communication campaigns (social networks, posters and many events).
Feuilleter ma collection qui rassemble des créations de branding et web pour vous offrir une vision complète de mon travail.
